EN: Forgiveness helps build harmonious relationships.

ZH: 她的真诚道歉得到了他的饶恕。
EN: Her sincere apology received his forgiveness.

ZH: 他向她表示饶恕，希望两人重新开始。
EN: He forgave her and hoped that they could start over.

